{"type": "article", "id": 17969, "title": "奶酪包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-24T07:20:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143058qJKvNjY69HxZWw2G.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t墨西哥的奶酪品牌 Karat 自 1980 年成立起只换过一次包装 ，且都是用红黄色调，这一次他们邀请设计事务所 Depot WPF 做全新的包装设计。 红黄分割的样式被保留了下来，另增加了深蓝、天蓝、棕色与黄色的搭配，使用圆圈、波浪等从奶牛身上提取的元素，有现代的设计感。重要的是，当这些图案排列放置时，能构成很有气势整体图画，有很强的广告效果。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143054Ifd4C1K3GjqYVRpu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061430557UpuEMb4doVGnlNW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143055vkDRm4i5HcgQaSXs.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143056BZEp7arjVqUYxMPl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143056TaP1WFC4twovd9V8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143057zLunXbRoxM8GDd7e.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}